import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='Year', y='Deaths', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the trend of deaths over the years?', wrap=True)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['Year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Year'], format='%Y', errors='ignore')
    chart = sns.barplot(x='Year', y='Deaths', hue='Entity', data=data, ci=None)
    chart.set_xticklabels(chart.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        chart.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the total number of deaths for each year?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
